data.description:
Located in the well-established Peachtree Estates in Bonaire, GA 31005 between Bonanza and Peach Blossom Roads, only minutes from Kroger, Chick-Fil-A, and many other shopping areas.  Includes 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, large dining room, spacious master and en-suite bathroom with jetted tub, dual vanities, shower, and walk-in closet.  Large custom kitchen cabinets with updated stainless steel appliances less than 5 years old.  Also features reverse osmosis water system in kitchen and full-house water filtration system.  Other features include:  Digital, programmable thermostat with multiple-room sensors; privacy-fenced  half-acre yard with gorgeous oak trees; convection microwave; large pantry; large laundry room; open floor plan; outdoor storage building; installed security system.  Don’t miss out on this quiet & well-located home!
* Seller’s Commission Offered.*
